 			<div class="section">
				<h1>Charlie Brooker on the Samsung E900 mobile phone</h1>
		   		    			    									   	This article appeared  on p5 of the <a href=http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2007/mar/05/g2  >G2</a> section of 					   	<a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian"  >the Guardian</a>
					   	on <time datetime="2007-03-05" pubdate><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/theguardian/2007/mar/05">Monday 5 March 2007</a></time>.
					   	It was published on
							<a href='http://www.guardian.co.uk/'>guardian.co.uk</a>
							at <time datetime="2007-03-05T00:00GMT" pubdate>00.13 GMT on Monday 5 March 2007</time>.
					   	It was last modified at <time datetime="2008-01-12T00:13GMT">00.13 GMT on Saturday 12 January 2008</time>.
						 It was first published at <time datetime="2007-03-05T08:33">08.33 GMT on Monday 5 March 2007</time>. 				   								</div>
