							<p>I once brought a samsung because it was pretty and pink and it was the crappiest phone ever. You can't put them on silent, I couldn't get any reception and it a program on it to record my menstural cycle. Oh, it also had a biorhythms chart and an annoying feature where the writing would come out all multicoloured and impossible to read. The moral of the story is to look around for phones and don't just fall for the pretty ones. And never ever get a samsung, they're all shit.</p>
						
