					<div class="comment-body">
						
							<p>Here's my 2c...
Find a brand you like and stick with it.
For me it's Nokia.  I never get seduced into even taking a cursory glance at anything else.  Yes, I know they are often boring, but there is usually some model that will satisfy you requirements and budget.  The payoff is (1) no bad surprises, (2) no learning curve to speak of, and in the case of Nokia (3) every pub, newsagent, whatever will have a charger you can use for a 10 minutes if you are in need - not to mention the five you have at home.</p>
						
